ditional purchase.</P>	<P><strong>USED</strong> - is product we have purchased through our trade in program or from other merchant partners. These products are carefully inspected before purchasing and tested to ensure they have <EM>full functionality</EM>. This product may not include additional discs, digital content, inserts or other inclusions typically associated with new product. All items are reconditioned and packaged for purchase. Select downloadable and online content/features may require an additional purchase. Used products may also include promotional items.</P>    </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="6" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_footer.jpg"></td>  </tr></table><table width="720" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top: 15px;">  <tr>    <td height="38" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_header.jpg"><h2 class="gh_pdp_box_header">Refunds, Returns and Exchanges</h2></td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_body.jpg" style="padding: 10px;">    	<strong>Exchanges<BR></strong>goHastings cannot perform product exchanges. Product may be returned for a refund if it meets the below criteria.</P>	<P class=content-p><strong>"New" Product Refund<BR></strong>You may return new, unopened items within 30 days of shipment for a full refund. Items should be returned in their original product packaging.</P>	<P class=content-p>Returns for defective Video Game Systems must be made through the manufacturers warranty.</P>	<P class=content-p>Shipping and handling charges are not refundable, unless the product is being returned due to our error.</P>	<P class=content-p>Return shipping will be paid by goHastings if the return is due to our error.</P>	<P class=content-p><strong>"USED/Previously Viewed Product (PV)" Refund<BR></strong>You may return used/previously viewed, unopened items within 30 days of shipment for a full refund. Items should be returned in their original product packaging.</P>	<P class=content-p>You may return used/previously viewed, defective items within 30 days of shipment for a full refund. Items should be returned in their opened original product packaging and include any manuals, cabling and accessories.</P>	<P class=content-p>Shipping and handling charges are not refundable, unless the product is being returned due to our error.</P>	<P class=content-p>Return shipping will be paid by goHastings if the return is due to our error.</P>	<P class=content-p><strong>Internet Purchase Return Instructions</strong><BR>	         Products purchased through goHastings may not be returned to a physical store location for refund. <BR>	         Refunds for products meeting the above mentioned return criteria should be handled as follows:</P>	<UL dir=ltr>	<LI>	<DIV class=content-p style="MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px"><em>Product returns due to our error or defective product:</em></DIV></LI></UL>	<BLOCKQUOTE dir=ltr style="MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px">	<P class=content-p dir=ltr style="MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px">Contact a Customer Service Representative at 1-877-427-8464 or send us a message via eBay messages for a return shipping label. Follow the instructions on the return shipping label to return the product. </P></BLOCKQUOTE>	<UL>	<LI>	<DIV class=content-p><em>All other Returns:</em></DIV></LI></UL>	<BLOCKQUOTE dir=ltr style="MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px">	<P class=content-p>Write the quantity and reason for return on the packing slip that came with your order. If you do not have your packing slip, please write the order number on a piece of paper and include with your return. Pack items securely, along with the packing slip as listed above.</P></BLOCKQUOTE>	<P class=content-p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ship your return to:<BR><STRONG>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hastings Internet, Inc<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3601 Plains Blvd.<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Amarillo, TX 79102</STRONG></P>	<P class=content-p><strong>Receiving a Refund<BR></strong>The refund will be processed after the product is received. Allow 2-3 weeks for your return to be received into our return center and a refund processed (though in many cases youll receive the refund sooner).&nbsp; Once we receive your return allow up to 2-5 days for your return to be received into our return center and a refund processed. If you notice discrepancies or have questions regarding your order, please call one of our Customer Service Representatives at 1-877-427-8464.</P>	<P class=content-p></P></DIV>    </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="6" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_footer.jpg"></td>  </tr></table><table width="720" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top: 15px;">  <tr>    <td height="38" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_header.jpg"><h2 class="gh_pdp_box_header">Cancellation Policy</h2></td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_body.jpg" style="padding: 10px;">    <p>We strive to fulfill every order we receive, however, on occasion we may have to cancel parts of your order due to availability of products. If your order is canceled, refunds will be issued within 2 to 5 business days to your PayPal account. 	<p>Up to date order information may be viewed in "My eBay". This will provide you with the most current information about your order''s status.</p>    </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="6" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_footer.jpg"></td>  </tr></table><table width="720" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;">  <tr>    <td height="38" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_header.jpg"><h2 class="gh_pdp_box_header">About Us</h2></td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td 