ng><BR>	         Products purchased through goHastings may not be returned to a physical store location for refund. <BR>	         Refunds for products meeting the above mentioned return criteria should be handled as follows:</P>	<UL dir=ltr>	<LI>	<DIV class=content-p style="MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px"><em>Product returns due to our error or defective product:</em></DIV></LI></UL>	<BLOCKQUOTE dir=ltr style="MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px">	<P class=content-p dir=ltr style="MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px">Contact a Customer Service Representative at 1-877-427-8464 or send us a message via eBay messages for a return shipping label. Follow the instructions on the return shipping label to return the product. </P></BLOCKQUOTE>	<UL>	<LI>	<DIV class=content-p><em>All other Returns:</em></DIV></LI></UL>	<BLOCKQUOTE dir=ltr style="MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px">	<P class=content-p>Write the quantity and reason for return on the packing slip that came with your order. If you do not have your packing slip, please write the order number on a piece of paper and include with your return. Pack items securely, along with the packing slip as listed above.</P></BLOCKQUOTE>	<P class=content-p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ship your return to:<BR><STRONG>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hastings Internet, Inc<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3601 Plains Blvd.<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Amarillo, TX 79102</STRONG></P>	<P class=content-p><strong>Receiving a Refund<BR></strong>The refund will be processed after the product is received. Allow 2-3 weeks for your return to be received into our return center and a refund processed (though in many cases youll receive the refund sooner).&nbsp; Once we receive your return allow up to 2-5 days for your return to be received into our return center and a refund processed. If you notice discrepancies or have questions regarding your order, please call one of our Customer Service Representatives at 1-877-427-8464.</P>	<P class=content-p></P></DIV>    </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="6" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_footer.jpg"></td>  </tr></table><table width="720" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top: 15px;">  <tr>    <td height="38" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_header.jpg"><h2 class="gh_pdp_box_header">Cancellation Policy</h2></td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_body.jpg" style="padding: 10px;">    <p>We strive to fulfill every order we receive, however, on occasion we may have to cancel parts of your order due to availability of products. If your order is canceled, refunds will be issued within 2 to 5 business days to your PayPal account. 	<p>Up to date order information may be viewed in "My eBay". This will provide you with the most current information about your order''s status.</p>    </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="6" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_footer.jpg"></td>  </tr></table><table width="720" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;">  <tr>    <td height="38" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_header.jpg"><h2 class="gh_pdp_box_header">About Us</h2></td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_body.jpg" style="padding: 10px;">    <img src="http://www.gohastings.com/assets/images/cms/basket_banners_small/HastingsStore.jpg" alt="Hastings Entertainment" width="300" height="194" align="right" />	<p>Founded in 1968, Hastings Entertainment/goHastings, Inc. is a leading multimedia entertainment retailer that combines the sale of new and used books, videos, video games and CDs, and trends and consumer electronics merchandise, with the rental of videos and video games in a superstore format.</p>	<p>We currently operate 130 superstores,