: Do you offer discounts on bulk purchases?</strong></dt>          <dd>A: Not at this time.</dd>    </dl>    </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="6" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_footer.jpg"></td>  </tr></table><table width="720" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top: 15px;">  <tr>    <td height="38" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_header.jpg"><h2 class="gh_pdp_box_header">Payment Options</h2></td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_body.jpg" style="padding: 10px;">    <p>We accept immediate payment via US PayPal accounts. PayPal allows you to pay using a major credit card, debit card or direct transfer from your checking account.</p>	<img src="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/paypal-badge.gif" alt="" width="181" height="62" />        </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="6" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_footer.jpg"></td>  </tr></table><table width="720" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top: 15px;">  <tr>    <td height="38" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_header.jpg"><h2 class="gh_pdp_box_header">Sales Tax</h2></td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_body.jpg" style="padding: 10px;">    <p>Currently goHastings only charges sales tax in states where we have a physical presence. Sales taxes are calculated during the ordering process and will show tax charged for the delivery destination, based on current tax rates. Shipping charges may also be subject to tax in certain states.</p>    </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="6" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_footer.jpg"></td>  </tr></table><table width="720" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top: 15px;">  <tr>    <td height="38" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_header.jpg"><h2 class="gh_pdp_box_header">Shipping</h2></td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_body.jpg" style="padding: 10px;">    <p>goHastings has partnered with the USPS and UPS to deliver your packages. We will determine the shipper at our discretion. We offer delivery to continental United States, Hawaii, Alaska, APO, FPO, and US territories.</p>	<p>Please note that your order will be shipped within 3 days of receiving cleared payment. Product may ship from multiple locations and arrive in separate packaging. Unless otherwise stated, standard shipping is used and delivery will take 3-10 working days, depending on the item purchased and the delivery location. NOTE: We are unable to offer combined shipping for multiple items purchased. This is because our items may ship from different locations.<br />      <br />      If any of the items on your order are shipped using <strong>UPS Mail Innovations</strong>, please see the FAQs on the <a href="http://www.upsmailinnovations.com/support/frequentlyaskedquestions.html" target="_blank"><strong>UPS Mail Innovations</strong></a> website. These tracking numbers will begin with the number <strong>92</strong>. Topics include: <a href="http://www.upsmailinnovations.com/support/frequentlyaskedquestions.html" target="_blank">Why is my tracking information unavailable? When will I receive my mail piece?</a></p>    </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="6" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_footer.jpg"></td>  </tr></table><table width="720" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top: 15px;">  <tr>    <td height="38" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_header.jpg"><h2 class="gh_pdp_box_header">100% Product Guarantee*</h2></td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_body.jpg" style="padding: 10px;">	<P>We strive to provide high quality products to our customers.</P>	<P><strong>New Product<BR></strong>We 100% GUARANTEE all new products to be in new condition and in the original packaging. </P>	<P><strong>*Exception:</strong> Video Games - In our retail locations, we remove the original packaging from some video games so that we can securely display the box. Therefore, a small number of video games may be repackaged with all of the original contents, in a plastic bag with an orange and white card stating that the item is a repackaged item. The product is still 100% GUARANTEED.</P>	<P><strong>USED/Previously Viewed Product<BR></strong>We 100% GUARANTEE the <EM>full functionality</EM> of all used and previously viewed product. Due to the nature of used and previously viewed products; booklet inserts, digital content and manuals are not guaranteed in any used or previously viewed product. Select downloadable and online content/features may require an additional purchase.</P>	<P><strong>Previously Viewed/Previously Played (PV/PP)</strong> - are movies/games that were rented in our retail locations. These movies/games have been reconditioned. This product will not include special features, additional discs, digital content, inserts or other inclusions typically associated with new product. Select downloadable and online content/features may require an additional purchase.</P>	<P><strong>USED</strong> - is product we have purchased through our trade in program or from other merchant partners. These products are carefully inspected before purchasing and tested to ensure they have <EM>full functionality</EM>. This product may not include additional discs, digital content, inserts or other inclusions typically associated with new product. All items are reconditioned and packaged for purchase. Select downloadable and online content/features may require an additional purchase. Used products may also include promotional items.</P>    </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="6" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_footer.jpg"></td>  </tr></table><table width="720" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top: 15px;">  <tr>    <td height="38" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_header.jpg"><h2 class="gh_pdp_box_header">Refunds, Returns and Exchanges</h2></td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_body.jpg" style="padding: 10px;">    	<strong>Exchanges<BR></strong>goHastings cannot perform product exchanges. Product may be returned for a refund if it meets the below criteria.</P>	<P class=content-p><strong>"New" Product Refund<BR></strong>You may return new, unopened items within 30 days of shipment for a full refund. Items should be returned in their original product packaging.</P>	<P class=content-p>Returns for defective Video Game Systems must be made through the manufacturers warranty.</P>	<P class=content-p>Shipping and handling charges are not refundable, unless the product is being returned due to our error.</P>	<P class=content-p>Return shipping will be paid by goHastings if the return is due to our error.</P>	<P class=content-p><strong>"USED/Previously Viewed Product (PV)" Refund<BR></strong>You may return used/previously viewed, unopened items within 30 days of shipment for a full refund. Items should be returned in their original product packaging.</P>	<P class=content-p>You may return used/previously viewed, defective items within 30 days of shipment for a full refund. Items should be returned in their opened original product packaging and include any manuals, cabling and accessories.</P>	<P class=content-p>Shipping and handling charges are not refundable, unless the product is being returned due to our error.</P>	<P class=content-p>Return shipping will be paid by goHastings if the return is due to our error.</P>	<P class=content-p><strong>Internet Purchase Return Instructions</strong><BR>	         Products purchased through goHastings may not be returned to a physical store location for refund. <BR>	         Refunds for products meeting the above mentioned return criteria should be handled as follows:</P>	<UL dir=ltr>	<LI>	<DIV class=content-p style="MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px"><em>Product returns due to our error or defective product:</em></DIV></LI></UL>	<BLOCKQUOTE dir=ltr style="MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px">	<P class=content-p dir=ltr style="MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px">Contact a Customer Service Representative at 1-877-427-8464 or send us a message via eBay messages for a return shipping label. Follow the instructions on the return shipping label to return the product. </P></BLOCKQUOTE>	<UL>	<LI>	<DIV class=content-p><em>All other Returns:</em></DIV></LI></UL>	<BLOCKQUOTE dir=ltr style="MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px">	<P class=content-p>Write the quantity and reason for return on the packing slip that came with your order. If you do not have your packing slip, please write the order number on a piece of paper and include with your return. Pack items securely, along with the packing slip as listed above.</P></BLOCKQUOTE>	<P class=content-p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ship your return to:<BR><STRONG>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hastings Internet, Inc<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3601 Plains Blvd.<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Amarillo, TX 79102</STRONG></P>	<P class=content-p><strong>Receiving a Refund<BR></strong>The refund will be processed after the product is received. Allow 2-3 weeks for your return to be received into our return center and a refund processed (though in many cases youll receive the refund sooner).&nbsp; Once we receive your return allow up to 2-5 days for your return to be received into our return center and a refund processed. If you notice discrepancies or have questions regarding your order, please call one of our Customer Service Representatives at 1-877-427-8464.</P>	<P class=content-p></P></DIV>    </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="6" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_footer.jpg"></td>  </tr></table><table width="720" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top: 15px;">  <tr>    <td height="38" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_header.jpg"><h2 class="gh_pdp_box_header">Cancellation Policy</h2></td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_body.jpg" style="padding: 10px;">    <p>We strive to fulfill every order we receive, however, on occasion we may have to cancel parts of your order due to availability of products. If your order is canceled, refunds will be issued within 2 to 5 business days to your PayPal account. 	<p>Up to date order information may be viewed in "My eBay". This will provide you with the most current information about your order''s status.</p>    </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="6" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_footer.jpg"></td>  </tr></table><table width="720" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;">  <tr>    <td height="38" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_header.jpg"><h2 class="gh_pdp_box_header">About Us</h2></td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_body.jpg" style="padding: 10px;">    <img src="http://www.gohastings.com/assets/images/cms/basket_banners_small/HastingsStore.jpg" alt="Hastings Entertainment" width="300" height="194" align="right" />	<p>Founded in 1968, Hastings Entertainment/goHastings, Inc. is a leading multimedia entertainment retailer that combines the sale of new and used books, videos, video games and CDs, and trends and consumer electronics merchandise, with the rental of videos and video games in a superstore format.</p>	<p>We currently operate 130 superstores, averaging approximately 24,000 square feet, primarily in medium-sized markets throughout the United States. We also operate two concept stores, Sun Adventure Sports in Amarillo, TX and Lubbock, TX as well as TradeSmart in Littleton, CO.</p>	<p>Hastings Entertainment/goHastings is a publicly traded company on NASDAQ under the symbol HAST.</p>    </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="6" background="http://images.gohastings.com/web/ebay/images/pdp_box_footer.jpg"></td>  </tr></table>        </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td colspan="2">    <div id="gh_pdp_footer">      <div style="margin: 0 8px 0 8px;">		<div style="width:740px;display:block;float:left;">&copy; 2011 Hastings Entertainment Inc.</div>		  <div style="width:200px;display:block;float:left;text-align: right;" class="store_link">  			<a href="http://stores.ebay.com/gohastings" class="gh_pdp_footer_links">    		Visit Our Store <img src="http://q.ebaystatic.com/aw/pics/icon/iconStoresNW_20x20.gif" alt="" height="20" width="20" align="absmiddle" border="0" />  			</a>		  </div>	  </div>    </div>    </td>  </tr></table></body></html>
